@prefix : <https://www.somusicvocabulary.org/music#> .
@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .

# NEGATIVE: :MusicianShape — a musician must play at least one instrument
# (singing counts via :Voice). This one plays nothing.
#
# Expected: Warning (the shape carries node-level sh:severity sh:Warning). A gate keyed
# on Violation COUNT would pass this fixture while appearing to test it.

:NEG_SilentMusician a :Musician ;
    rdfs:label "Negative fixture — a musician who plays nothing"@en ;
    .
